OL,3,CHealth Minister Mike Nesbitt warns of
OL,4,C'catastrophic' cuts
OL,6,FNorthern Ireland's Health Minister has
OL,7,Fwarned that the service could be
OL,8,Ffacing a year of "catastrophic" cuts
OL,9,Fand further industrial action.
OL,11,FMike Nesbitt was briefing Stormont's
OL,12,Fhealth committee about the
OL,13,Fdepartment's financial situation.
OL,15,FThe funding gap is currently estimated
OL,16,Fat around #400 million for 2025/26.
OL,18,FHe described a situation that will be
OL,19,F"impossible" if his department does
OL,20,Fnot receive "significant" allocations
OL,21,Fin in-year monitoring rounds.
