OL,3,CHealth Minister Mike Nesbitt warns of
OL,4,C'catastrophic' cuts
OL,6,FAppearing before the Stormont Health
OL,7,FCommittee on Thursday afternoon, Mr
OL,8,FNesbitt warned of significant
OL,9,Fincreases in costs, including pay and
OL,10,Fprice inflation, increased national
OL,11,Finsurance contributions for GPs,
OL,12,Fpharmacists and social care providers,
OL,13,Fand rising demand.
OL,15,FMr Nesbitt is aiming to plug the
OL,16,Fprojected #400m gap by the health
OL,17,Ftrusts finding #200m in new savings
OL,18,Fand allocations from in-year
OL,19,Fmonitoring funds.
