OL,3,CHealth Minister Mike Nesbitt warns of
OL,4,C'catastrophic' cuts
OL,6,FBut he warned that finding that level
OL,7,Fof savings is "ambitious and very
OL,8,Fchallenging".
OL,10,FMr Nesbitt also pointed out that the
OL,11,Fdraft Northern Ireland budget provides
OL,12,Fno additional funding for waiting list
OL,13,Freduction initiatives for the second
OL,14,Fconsecutive year, and referred to
OL,15,Freports which have found the health
OL,16,Fand social care service needs more
OL,17,Ffunding.
