OL,3,CHealth Minister Mike Nesbitt warns of
OL,4,C'catastrophic' cuts
OL,6,FHe urged MLAs on the health committee
OL,7,Fagainst "traditional tit-for-tat
OL,8,Fexchanges", as well as calls for
OL,9,Fefficiencies to be found as well as
OL,10,Fmore funding to be directed into
OL,11,Fspecific areas.
OL,13,F"The stark reality is that we need to
OL,14,Fbe honest about the current and
OL,15,Fprojected demand pressures on health
OL,16,Fand social care," he said.
