OL,3,CHealth Minister Mike Nesbitt warns of
OL,4,C'catastrophic' cuts
OL,6,F"Frankly, there needs to be a reality
OL,7,Fcheck. The notion that our health
OL,8,Fbudget should not grow any further is
OL,9,Fdelusion on stilts. Demand is always
OL,10,Fgrowing and the pressure for increased
OL,11,Fspending across many different
OL,12,Fservices is immense, and members, I
OL,13,Fbelieve, from all parties know this.
OL,15,F"Because when they are not telling me
OL,16,Fto live within my budget and suck it
OL,17,Fup, they are calling on me to spend
OL,18,Fmore across a vast range of areas.
OL,19,FThat's part of the pressure.
OL,26,@nD@AOUwD@AOU
