OL,3,CHealth Minister Mike Nesbitt warns of
OL,4,C'catastrophic' cuts
OL,6,F"If we want to get waiting lists down,
OL,7,Fthat will require investment. If we
OL,8,Fwant more care outside of hospital,
OL,9,Fthat will require investment. If we
OL,10,Fwant to invest more in staffing, that
OL,11,Ftoo comes with a price."
OL,13,FHe referred to official projections
OL,14,Fthat the population aged 65 and over
OL,15,Fis projected to increase by 49.6%
OL,16,Fbetween mid-2022 and mid-2047, and the
OL,17,Fnumber of over-85s is projected to
OL,18,Fincrease by 122.2% over the same
OL,19,Fperiod.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@XO]
