OL,3,CHealth Minister Mike Nesbitt warns of
OL,4,C'catastrophic' cuts
OL,6,F"Increased life expectancy is a
OL,7,Fmassive achievement for society and
OL,8,Fmodern science but when it comes to
OL,9,Finescapable realities for public
OL,10,Fservices and public spending, older
OL,11,Fpeople need more health care and more
OL,12,Fsocial care,"
OL,14,F"Demand will grow very sharply and
OL,15,Fthat has massive budgetary
OL,16,Fimplications.
