OL,6,F"Yes, we can do things differently. In
OL,7,Fsome areas we can slow the increase in
OL,8,Fcosts but let's not pretend we can
OL,9,Freduce or virtually freeze health
OL,10,Fspending while providing the level of
OL,11,Fservices we want and that the public
OL,12,Fdemand."
